criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Hospitalized for primary diagnosis of HF;

          2. Anticipated to be discharged home;

          3. Agreeable to longitudinal post-discharge care at Cleveland Clinic Main Campus in the
             first few weeks after hospital discharge;

          4. Patient or an individual in their social support network has the ability (equipment
             and connectivity) to do a virtual visit after hospital discharge;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Being transferred to another hospital, or being discharged to an inpatient facility or
             nursing home;

          2. Being discharged to hospice;

          3. Subject currently enrolled in an interventional research study that requires an
             in-person clinical visit within 7 days post-discharge.
